119
00:08:53,545 --> 00:08:55,047
Base color textures are clean

120
00:08:55,207 --> 00:08:58,150
with correct video values and low contrast.

121
00:08:58,851 --> 00:09:00,352
Roughness is richer on information,

122
00:09:00,392 --> 00:09:03,736
but always avoiding that pixel grainy noise.

123
00:09:04,887 --> 00:09:09,133
