142
00:10:14,410 --> 00:10:17,492
And you can finally check that the mesh corners are rounded.

143
00:10:18,732 --> 00:10:21,333
But the normal map doesn't have any hypo-information vector.

144
00:10:22,590 --> 00:10:26,294
This is because I used on this asset the medium polyworkflow.

145
00:10:28,737 --> 00:10:33,422
This workflow has been used on Island Isolation and Star Citizen, between others.

146
00:10:33,522 --> 00:10:37,066
They are all games with big objects, big assets and surfaces.

147
00:10:38,608 --> 00:10:44,394
It's based on the creation of soft bevels for the corners, avoiding the hard edges and the low poly look.

148
00:10:45,752 --> 00:10:49,434
And we realized that we are not only saving textures here

149
00:10:49,555 --> 00:10:52,296
and draw calls with this method, but also getting

150
00:10:52,336 --> 00:10:53,937
a better pixel resolution.

151
00:10:56,919 --> 00:11:00,461
We have this way less seams, more tiling textures,

152
00:11:00,841 --> 00:11:03,603
